card0.name: Pikachu
card0.description: Pikachu that can generate powerful electricity have cheek sacs that are extra soft and super stretchy.

card1.name: Charizard
card1.description: It spits fire that is hot enough to melt boulders. It may cause forest fires by blowing flames.

card3.name: Squirtle
card3.description: After birth, its back swells and hardens into a shell. Powerfully sprays foam from its mouth.

65a3c154deb0f.name: Metapod
65a3c154deb0f.description: MetapodStats HP Attack Defense Special Attack Special Defense Speed> It is waiting for the moment to evolve. At this stage, it can only harden, so it remains motionless to avoid attack.

65a65c5c78c35.name: Blastoise
65a65c5c78c35.description: It crushes its foe under its heavy body to cause fainting. In a pinch, it will withdraw inside its shell.

65ad1840be0e0.name: Bulbasaur
65ad1840be0e0.description: A strange seed was planted on its back at birth. The plant sprouts and grows with this POKéMON.

65ad19758a9c9.name: Caterpie
65ad19758a9c9.description: Its short feet are tipped with suction pads that enable it to tirelessly climb slopes and walls.

65ad198d5a924.name: ivysaur
65ad198d5a924.description: When the bulb on its back grows large, it appears to lose the ability to stand on its hind legs.

65ad19a5a72f7.name: Weedle
65ad19a5a72f7.description: Often found in forests, eating leaves. It has a sharp venomous stinger on its head.

65ad1a414d61c.name: Nidoran
65ad1a414d61c.description: Females are more sensitive to smells than males. While foraging, they’ll use their whiskers to check wind direction and stay downwind of predators.
